dom despite freedom is power.', 35554, 0), (194318, 'Its only called PTDS if you stop fighting.', 35554, 0), (194319, 'Read something worth writing about or write something worth reading about', 33, 0), (194320, 'You have this thing called a life. Its only you that gets to live it and you only get to do it one time', 35555, 0), (194321, 'No dream is too big to come true.You are born to manifest the glory of God on earth.', 2878, 0), (194322, 'Motivate yourself, you can be great.', 2878, 0), (194323, 'Unlike the rest of nature, our mission in life is not etched in stone. We can choose our destiny, and we do, either by design or default, by taking control of our lives’ or relinquishing it to others.', 35556, 0), (194324, 'Born to fly, endless possibilities.', 2878, 0), (194325, 'There are two types of obstacles in life', 35557, 0), (194326, 'Life is about the journey, not the destination. As long as we persevere in mindful thinking, beliefs and actions, our internal compass will point us towards true-self each step of the way.', 35556, 0), (194327, 'Many embrace the concepts of life and liberty; yet shirk its consequent responsibilities; the first notion being an inalienable right, the latter, an insufferable wrong.', 35556, 0), (194328, 'You have to believe in your dreams, to reach out for your dreams.', 2878, 0), (194329, 'A DESPERATE MAN,HE''S A READY-MADE VICTIM', 35558, 0), (194330, 'Listening', 35559, 0), (194331, 'The answer to why we exist does not exist, at least not where most of us look for it. We must look inward not out. We should not ask this question of life, but rather of ourselves - and then answer it.', 35556, 0), (194332, 'Maintain balance in life; not unlike a tire, a life out of balance results in a rough ride and needless wear and tear.', 35556, 0), (194333, 'Every problem has a solution, even if we do not know the answer', 35560, 0), (194334, 'Dream big, you are powerful.You can exceed all your expectations', 2878, 0), (194335, 'Either You see G