e I had slept the last few months away and now, suddently, I was waking up.', 35851, 0), (195788, 'You are sweet to be so concerned over my love life, but I’ve decided only to date guys who have bigger swords than me.', 35849, 0), (195789, 'I blew through her like baby’s breath through a dandelion, and my soulleft its mark on hers. Forever. In one night, I’d bound her too me for as longas she lived, and I had no words to tell her.When I woke the next night, to see her there, above me, the relief radiatingfrom every line of her body, I thought it was more of a miracle than myfirst rising.', 6036, 0), (195790, 'Tonight I had wrought magic powerful enough to have drawn the attention of a goddess. In that moment, though, I was certain of one thing: Of all the magic I possessed, none of it could begin to compare to the magic he and I created together.', 35852, 0), (195791, 'I want to leave all my friends and the sunlight for a small, rainy town.', 2359, 0), (195792, 'You have to let go of your past Keira. These scars you hold are only skin deep, they do not connect to your heart or your soul. These scars do not define you, you define them. They do not represent death and destruction like you think, they represent life, the life you chose to want to live... so... make it worth it.', 35844, 0), (195793, 'Laire, get back here! You do not drink before we meet with our mortal enemy.', 35849, 0), (195794, 'Life is a ride that we take, sometimes with a passenger, other timesall alone. How you bounce back from life tells a lot about you as aperson. Some people fight to the death, others are more a part of deathand never truly understand why this is so……', 3020, 0), (195795, 'I write for the same reason I eat chocolate - because it is, undeniably a compulsion.', 9826, 0), (195796, 'Paranormal romance gives me the opportunity to explore love outside of its traditional boundaries. Common themes are hunger and uncontrollable desires, but I like to push further into wounds that canno